title: Call.of.Duty.4-Modern.Warfare.Repack-P2P
description:
General Information:
Year of release : 2007
Genre : Action (Shooter) / 3D / 1st Person
Developer : Infinity Ward
Publisher : Activision Publication
Type : Repack
Language : English Voice set Language : English only
Crack : enclosing

System requirements:
Operating system: Windows 7 / Vista / XP
Processor: Pentium or AMD 2.4 GHz
Memory: 512MB RAM
Video: 128 Mb
Sound Card: Sound Card compatible with DirectX 9.0
Hard disk space: 8 GB

Description:
The fourth part of the popular series in the world, where players are invited to get acquainted with the intricacies of politics and military affairs of the beginning of the XXI century. The plot will hold the players to the Middle East, Eastern Europe and will throw together with American and British special forces in Russia. Since the action is these days, the soldiers not only hung with the most modern weapons, but also a variety sverhtehnologichny gadgets. Call of Duty 4 has been highly appreciated by specialists, having received the world-famous exhibition E3 2007 the title of "best shooter"
